nt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 4aAntisemitismus. 4aFrankfurt am Main. 4aJüdisches Leben. 4aStadtgeschichte.  aFrankfurt am Main.  aJewish life.  aantisemitism.  aurban history.1 aAtlan, Eva, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBerger-Dittscheid, Cornelia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrumlik, Micha, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBönisch, Edgar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDrummer, Heike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHeuberger, Rachel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHopp, Andrea, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKallenberg, Vera, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKiesel, Doron, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKonz, Britta, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKorn, Salomon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKrah, Franziska, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKrone, Kerstin von der, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKupferberg, Yael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLenhard, Philipp, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMorgenstern, Matthias, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNashman Fraiman, Susan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchneider-Ludorff, Gury, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSeemann, Birgit, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSpäter, Jörg, econtribu